**BtcPool.ru**, is a [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]].

BtcPool.ru's Mining Pool uses own scoring system.

To calculate users payouts we use eleven randomly choosen shares from all shares at current round. That is, if you send at least one share, you get a chance to earn 25 à¸¿. The more you send the shares, the greater will be your chance to win at current round.


|Share |Bitcoins
|---|---
|1 |25 BTC
|2 |12.5 BTC
|3 |5.25 BTC
|4 |3.15 BTC
|5 |1.57 BTC
|6 |0.78 BTC
|7 |0.39 BTC
|8 |0.19 BTC
|9 |0.09 BTC
|10 |0.04 BTC
|11 |0.02 BTC
|12-.. |1/(number of members)

